    "photo_3_11": "<strong>Pastor Huntley & Kim Young-bok</strong>, <em>Victims transported to Gwangju Christian Hospital after mass shooting by martial law troops, May 21, 1980, Color negative, 24 x 36 mm</em>, May 18 Archives",
    "photo_3_12": "<strong>Choi Byung-oh</strong>, <em>City view taken from a telephone booth near the provincial government headquarters (Gwangju Do cheong), shortly after the fierce fighting of the afternoon, May 21, 1980, 24x36 mm black and white negative, Gwangju</em>, May 18 Archives",
